@startuml
title Szenario 5: Zusammenbau der Puzzleteile

' Breite erzwingen
skinparam ParticipantPadding 60
skinparam BoxPadding 10
hide footbox

participant "Input" as IN
participant "Preparation" as PREP
participant "Anchor\nSelection" as ANCHOR
participant "Piece\nPlacement" as PLACE
participant "Visualization" as VIS
participant "Output" as OUT

IN -> PREP: edge_solver_results\n(chains, connections)

' Schritte 1 & 2 zusammengefasst
PREP -> PREP: 1. Calc centroids &\n2. Normalize (blue dots ↑)

PREP -> ANCHOR: Prepared pieces

ANCHOR -> ANCHOR: 3. Select anchor\n(highest score)

ANCHOR -> PLACE: 4. Place anchor at origin\n(T₀ = {pos:0,0, rot:calc})

loop for piece 1 to N-1
    PLACE -> PLACE: 5. Find best connection\n(to placed pieces)

    ' HIER SPAREN WIR PLATZ:
    ' Schritte 6 & 7 (Mathe) in eine Notiz ausgelagert
    note right of PLACE
      **Transformation (Schritte 6-7):**
      6. Translate: blue_dot → anchor_blue_dot
      7. Rotate: align red_dot with anchor_red_dot
      Store: Tᵢ = {pos, rot}
    end note
end

PLACE -> VIS: All pieces placed

' Schritt 8 (Liste) in eine Notiz ausgelagert
note right of VIS
  **8. Generate 8 steps:**
  - Centroids & Orientations
  - Anchor selection & Placement
  - Placements (1-4)
  - Complete assembly
end note

VIS -> OUT: assembly_steps_combined.png

@enduml